about: I am Dylan Kolak, a 21 year old from New York who is on the Mens Gymnastics team at the University of Illinois. I have been a social media creator for the last 3 years on Tiktok and Instagram with around 730,000 followers on Tiktok and 60,000 followers on Instagram. I am very interested in working and collaborating with companies to promote their brand on my social media platforms. I am very flexible with the types of brands I would work with. Primarily I am interested in Fitness, Fashion, Photography, Food/drink, Travel, Lifestyle, Ocean conservation, and Environmentalism. I am also studying Marine Biology with a minor in acting and filmmaking at the University of Illinois. I am currently a Senior, but I have 5 years of eligibility so I will be competing for UIUC for another year.
heading: Fitness/fashion/lifestyle content creator and D1 Gymnast at UIUC
name: Dylan Kolak
